channel.title: Hi, i got a problem running moparscape, help pl0x?
channel.description:
Sup, when i click on run moparscape (i have already extracted it to desktop), when i run it, it says:
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.UnsupportedClassVersionError: Bot <Unsupported major.minor version 49.0> at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass0<Native Method> at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass<Unknown Source> at java.security.SecureClassLoader.defineClass<Unknown Source> at java.net.URLClassLoader.defineCLass<Unknown Source> at java.net.URLClassLoader.acces$100<Unknown Source> at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run<Unknown Source> at java.security.AccesController.doPrivileged<Native Method> at java.net.URLClassLoader.findCLass<Unknown Source> at java.lang.CLassLoader.loadClass<Unknown Source> at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass<Unknown Source> at java.lang.CLassLoader.loadClass<Unknown Source> at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClassInternal<Unknown Source> click any key to continue....
and then i click and it closes!
What shall i do? i really want to play :confused:
